comments: Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Eskdale.

That part which until 1.4.1935 formed part of the parish of 
    Millom Without. See also Table 2, note (b).
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Waberthwaite.

Created 1.4.1934 out of the parishes of Eskdale & Wasdale and 
    Birker & Austhwaite. See also Table 2, note (d).

Abolished 1.4.1934 and divided between the parishes of Eskdale 
    and Nether Wasdale. See also Table 2, note (e).

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of MIllom. Abolished 
    1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Millom Without.

Created 1.4.1934 out of the parishes of Millom Rural. See also 
    Table 2, notes (b), (c) and (d).

    Drigg & Carleton. See also Table 2, note (a).
Abolished 1.4.1934 and added to the parish of Whicham.
